Easy Blog Application for Rails Learners (Yeni baslayanlar icin kolay blog) 
----------------------------------------

1- This blog baesed on rails 3.1.1. 
2- See online here http://garalo.tk/
3- Detail explanation is here, http://blog.bryanbibat.net/2011/09/24/starting-a-professional-rails-3-1-app-with-web-app-theme-devise-and-kaminari/
4- you will learn  accepts_nested_attributes_for, migrations, and active records, relations ( has_many, belongs_to etc.)
5- This blog contains blog entry, comments, categories and tags.( Also you will learn, how you can do it) 
6- This blog is not complated. I WANT YOUR HELP. Also if you are beginner no problem. Please don`t hesitate. You can checkout it and customise and put your code.
7- I want to add authentication with cancan, image upload(file upload), active_admin and maybe better desing or using free web templates. if you know one of them, PLEASE PUT YOUR CODE and SHARE HERE.

( Eger rails ogrenmek isteyenler icin yazilmis bir program. Eger katilmak isterseniz lutfen cekinmeden kodlarinizi burada paylasabilirsiniz. Yanlis veya dogru diye yargilamak degil sadece paylasmak onemli deiyenler icin yazilmis bir programdir. Buradan calisan haline ulasabilirsiniz. garalo.tk )



